title: League of Legends Stats Analysis
description: A comprehensive analysis of the League of Legends game statistics. The project aims to provide insights into the game's performance, visualizing the data, and predicting matching outcomes.

title: Expository Visualization
description: An expository visualization that discover the trends of the sunshine hours in U.S major cities.

title: Python Image Processing
description: Using Python to apply image filter such as grayscale, negation, and brightness adjustment.
